org.ireas.mediawiki

Class ApiConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ireas.mediawiki.ApiConstants

  • public final class ApiConstants
extends Object
    Provides constants used by the MediaWiki API, e. g. the names of the parameters, keywords and the name of result fields. For a detailed explanation of the values, consult the MediaWiki API documentation.
